  "name": "RPlog_A_Second_Attack",
  "title": "A Second Attack",
  "summary": "On a neon-lit evening in the New Alderaan district of Ord Mantell, the freshly released fugitive Gustaf Heram crosses paths with several people who had helped him before -- the doctor Lynae and her bodyguard Draygo, the pilot Ranma, the eccentric Foerga, and the wry Kalna -- as the combat medic Galatea drifts past unnoticed. The reunion is shattered when a hulking kidnapper seizes Gustaf at gunpoint, threatening a thermal detonator and dragging his hostage toward a getaway speeder to recover three million credits Gustaf stole. The group draws weapons; Ranma slashes the detonator from the kidnapper's hand, others blast the speeder, and after a running brawl Gustaf -- coming to and fighting back -- and his rescuers finally subdue the attacker, with Gustaf himself burying a knife in the man's shoulder. As the authorities arrive late, Lynae, Kalna, and Ranma corner Gustaf at a bistro and press him to explain. He reveals he is Margrave Gustaf Heram of Vandelhelm, who took the money from the criminal Vandelhelm Cooperation Syndicate to buy weapons and free his Imperial-occupied homeworld, and the women agree to help connect him with a senator and arms contacts in hopes of supporting his rebellion.",
